==Japanese==
===Etymology===
[[平]] (へい, ''hei'': "even", "steady", "flat") + [[安]] (あん, ''an'': "peace", "ease")

===Noun===
{{janoun|へいあん|heian}}

# [[peace]]

===Proper noun===
{{janoun|へいあん|Heian}}

# Abbreviation of [[平安時代]] ([[へいあんじだい]], ''Heian jidai''), the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]] of Japanese history.

===Adjective===
'''平安な''' (へいあんな, heian na)

# [[peaceful]]

===Adverb===
'''平安に''' (へいあんに, heian ni)

# [[peacefully]]

